 <!-- / -->
    <div class="container col-md-10 safety-accordion" target="#sfty-acc3">
                <span class="safety-spoiler">▼</span> 
                Biosafety Cabinets. 
            </div>
            <div class="container col-md-9 safety-panel"    id="sfty-acc3">
                   <p> Our lab is equipped with 4 Biosafety Cabinets, which prevent the samples we work with from contamination caused by either ourselves or  external agents. As part of our protocols, we always turn on the UV light for 15 minutes minimum before using the biosafety cabinets, and we also clean our hands and the materials we will introduce with 70% ethanol. Finally, when done using the biosafety cabinets, we make sure to clean them and let the UV light sterilize them for another 15 minutes.

                    </p>
                <div class="row acc-images">
                    <img src="/img/portrait_placeolder.png" alt="img" class="safety-acc-img">
